@startuml
actor "User" as U
participant "Reporting System" as RS
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Scheduler" as SCH

U -> RS: Request Report (type, format)
RS -> DB: Fetch Data
DB --> RS: Data Retrieved
RS -> RS: Generate Report
U -> RS: Export Report
RS -> U: Deliver PDF/Excel Report

== Scheduled Report ==
SCH -> RS: Trigger Report Generation
RS -> DB: Fetch Data
DB --> RS: Data Retrieved
RS -> RS: Generate Scheduled Report
RS -> U: Send Report by Email
@enduml
